movie.title: Alien Arrival
movie.description_intro: Kye's a prisoner of war caught between 2 armies; neither side of which he believes. When offered an opportunity for freedom, he sets out on one last rescue mission, only to become stranded on a desert moon, when his ship - the Arrowhead - crash lands. Kye has to learn to survive when a new life is discovered, which will challenge his beliefs.

movies.title: Scorcher
movies.summary: After a disastrous nuclear accident, scientists discover the Earth's tectonic plates are shifting and creating immense pressure that will destroy the Earth in a fiery global eruption, and it's up to a few top scientists to find a way to stop it.

movies.title: Chennai Express
movies.summary: Rahul embarks on a journey to a small town in Tamil Nadu to fulfill the last wish of his grandfather: to have his ashes immersed in the Holy water of Rameshwaram. En route, he meets a woman hailing from a unique family down South. As they find love through this journey in the exuberant lands of South India, an unanticipated drive awaits them.

movies.title: Headshot
movies.summary: Uwais plays a young man who washes ashore, an amnesiac with a serious head injury whose past comes back to haunt him shortly after being nursed back to health by a young doctor. Violence ensues. Sweet, sweet violence.

movies.title: It Came from the Desert
movies.summary: A pulpy, action monster movie, inspired by Cinemaware's cult 1980s video game "It Came from the Desert". A nostalgic tribute to creature features from the 1950's, It Came From The Desert features rival motocross heroes and heroines, kegger parties in the desert, secret underground military bases, romantic insecurities...and of course giant ants.
